# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Clean URLs (/unclaimed, /airline, /11ways, /eitc) are served automatically
# by Cloudflare Pages from the matching .html file — no redirect rules needed.
# (Adding /unclaimed -> /unclaimed.html caused an infinite loop because Pages
#  auto-strips .html back to the clean URL.)

# Per-video vanity CTA slugs -> their freebie opt-in page. Videos burn/print short URLs
# (/owed, /02, /taxcredits, numeric per-video) that have no .html of their own; without
# these, Pages falls back to the homepage/sales page and the promised freebie is lost.
# 302 (temporary) so slugs can be re-pointed later. Fixes V02 (/02) and protects V04 (/taxcredits).
/owed         /11ways     302
/01           /unclaimed  302
/02           /airline    302
/03           /11ways     302
/04           /eitc       302
/taxcredits   /eitc       302
